                    <lb n="1r27=27" break="no"/>r atiya mā malai pararāca rācamuṉi maturai turait-
                    <lb n="1r28=28" break="no"/> taṉam A<hi rend="grantha">ṣṭa</hi>-campaṉṉa-rācātirāyar tiṅkaḷc cut
                    <lb n="1r29=29" break="no"/>ta vaṅki<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi> piṟama-teṭcaṇā karaikki ceṅkōl uṭa
                    <lb n="1r30=30" break="no"/>ṉ ccel<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>u</reg></choice>tti yaruḷum cuvāmiyār avarkaḷāṉa 
                </p>
                <p>
                    <lb n="1r31=31"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> vicaiya kumāra muttureṅka cokkaliṅ
                    <lb n="1r32=32" break="no"/>ka tirumalai ṉāyakkar cuvāmiyār avarkaḷ tiruk
                    <lb n="1r33=33" break="no"/>karuṇai purintu
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    <hi rend="grantha">svē</hi>ta-natī-<hi rend="grantha">dakṣi</hi>ṇa-tīram ākiya p
                    <lb n="1r34=34" break="no"/>āṇṭi-ṉāṭṭi<choice><sic>s</sic><corr>l</corr></choice> miḻalaik kū<choice><orig>tt</orig><reg>ṟṟ</reg></choice>attil 
