                    <lb n="1v23=57" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha"><choice><sic>śo</sic><corr>ro</corr></choice></hi>kamum paṇṇiṉa tōṣattil pōkak kaṭavār ākavum
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    <lb n="1v24=58"/>cokkaliṅkam mīṉāṭci reṅkanāyakar Uccimalaippiḷḷaiya
                    <lb n="1v25=59" break="no"/> r māriyammaṉ paḻaṇi murukar potiya-māmalai Akattiya
